Ringier, Springer Stay Separate in Hungary, Vilaggazdasag Says

-- B y   Z o l t a n   S i m o n
-- 
2011-07-11T07:18:41Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-11/ringier-springer-stay-separate-in-hungary-vilaggazdasag-says.html
Switzerland’s Ringier AG and  Axel
Springer AG (SPR) , Europe’s largest newspaper publisher, must develop
“independent” strategies in  Hungary  after the local regulator
opposed their merger,  Vilaggazdasag  reported, citing an
interview with Jozsef Bayer, the chief executive officer of
Springer’s Hungarian unit.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Zoltan Simon in Budapest at 
 zsimon@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Zoltan Simon at 
 zsimon@bloomberg.net  